snippet.title: Chewy Butterscotch Graham Cookies
snippet.description: Watch everyone come running when they catch a heavenly whiff of these Chewy Butterscotch Graham Cookies. Get out the milk and have a treat.

snippet.title: Double Chocolate Peanut Butter Thumbprint Cookies
snippet.description: These peanut butter-filled chocolate thumbprint cookies are a must with a tall glass of ice-cold milk.
